<http://example.org/req/451#> a owl:Ontology .

<http://example.org/req/451#CatchCanType_EngineSystems> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000004>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000040>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Thing ;
    rdfs:label "Catch cans for the engine coolant system and engine lubrication system",
        "Catch cans for the engine coolant system and engine lubrication system"@en ;
